text: , better known by his ring name , was a Japanese professional wrestler. He wrestled on the independent circuit most of his career. He was best known for his steel cage matches in Frontier Martial-Arts Wrestling (FMW). Goto died from liver cancer on May 29, 2022 at the age of 58. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Deaths from liver cancer Category:Japanese professional wrestlers
